msgid "SELECT YOUR TACTICAL DOCTRINE:"
msgstr "SELECCIONA TU DOCTRINA:"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/date"
msgid "July 15th, 1944 · Belarus"
msgstr "15 de julio de 1944 - Bielorrusia"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/story"
msgid ""
"While the 1st Belorussian Front is smashing through Army Group Centre during "
"Operation Bagration in the summer of 1944, you are advancing behind the main "
"line of attack. Your orders are clear: report to the headquarters of the "
"17th Rifle Division"
msgstr ""
"Mientras el 1er Frente Bielorruso aplasta al Grupo de Ejércitos Centro "
"durante la Operación Bagration en el verano de 1944, tú avanzas por detrás "
"de la línea principal. Tus órdenes son claras: preséntate en el cuartel "
"general de la 17ª División de Fusileros"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/gameover_officer_dead"
msgid "Hauptmann Hellmann was killed."
msgstr "Hauptmann Hellmann fue asesinado."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/gameover_secret"
msgid "You unlocked the secret ending!"
msgstr "¡Has desbloqueado el final secreto!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/hint_docs"
msgid "Put the documents into Dietrich Hellmann's inventory to continue."
msgstr ""
"Pon los documentos en el inventario de Dietrich Hellmann para continuar."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/hint_secret"
msgid "Put the chicken steak into one of the boxes near the field kitchen."
msgstr ""
"Pon el filete de pollo en una de las cajas que hay cerca de la cocina de "
"campaña."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/name"
msgid "The Trap"
msgstr "La trampa"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/name_big"
msgid "The Trap"
msgstr "La trampa"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/chicken"
msgid ""
"I am quite hungry. Should we maybe bring this meat to our field kitchen for "
"later?"
msgstr ""
"Tengo bastante hambre. ¿Tal vez deberíamos llevar esta carne a nuestra "
"cocina de campaña para más tarde?"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/docs_found_01"
msgid ""
"Let's see... I can't make out all the details, but even at a first glance, "
"the news is grim. Discouraging, I'd say."
msgstr ""
"Veamos... No puedo distinguir todos los detalles, pero incluso a primera "
"vista, las noticias son malas. Desalentadoras, diría yo."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/docs_found_02"
msgid ""
"They've surrounded our division and plan to attack it from two directions. "
"There is more bad news - they've got heavy tanks!"
msgstr ""
"Han rodeado a nuestra división y planean atacarla desde dos direcciones. Hay "
"más malas noticias: ¡tienen tanques pesados!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/docs_found_03"
msgid ""
"The situation calls for guts and determination. We must ambush their "
"reinforcements and warn our comrades!"
msgstr ""
"La situación exige agallas y determinación. ¡Debemos tender una emboscada a "
"sus refuerzos y avisar a nuestros camaradas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/enemy_see_pl"
msgid ""
"Now they know we're here. In a moment, the whole village will be looking for "
"us. Prepare yourselves!"
msgstr ""
"Ahora saben que estamos aquí. Dentro de un momento, toda la aldea nos estará "
"buscando. ¡Preparaos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/evac_01"
msgid "I think that was the last of them. Amazing job, soldiers!"
msgstr "Creo que ése fue el último. ¡Un trabajo increíble, soldados!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/evac_02"
msgid "Let's get out of here. We need to warn our comrades."
msgstr "Salgamos de aquí. Tenemos que avisar a nuestros camaradas."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/intro_01"
msgid "We're almost there. The 17th Division HQ should be somewhere nearby."
msgstr ""
"Ya casi hemos llegado. El Cuartel General de la 17ª División debería estar "
"cerca."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/intro_02"
msgid "These places are so beautiful... Aren't they?"
msgstr "Estos lugares son tan bonitos... ¿A que sí?"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/intro_03"
msgid "What do you think? Will the 17th Division be glad to see us?"
msgstr "¿Qué te parece? ¿Se alegrará de vernos la 17ª División?"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/intro_04"
msgid "A soviet tank? Mein Gott! It's a trap!"
msgstr "¿Un tanque soviético? ¡Mein Gott! ¡Es una trampa!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/intro_05"
msgid ""
"I'll tell you what's going on. Partisans in German uniforms are taking our "
"comrades prisoner."
msgstr ""
"Te diré lo que está pasando. Partisanos con uniformes alemanes están "
"haciendo prisioneros a nuestros camaradas."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/intro_06"
msgid ""
"Don't panic. Let's think. I assume you don't want to join the guys with "
"raised hands?"
msgstr ""
"Que no cunda el pánico. Pensemos. ¿Supongo que no quieres unirte a ellos con "
"las manos arriba?"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/intro_07"
msgid ""
"First of all, let's keep quiet for some time. The Soviets outnumber us, and "
"they have much better equipment. We must find a gap in their defense and use "
"their weapons against them. Once they spot us, the whole village will attack "
"us."
msgstr ""
"En primer lugar, guardemos silencio durante algún tiempo. Los soviéticos nos "
"superan en número y tienen mucho mejor equipamiento. Debemos encontrar una "
"brecha en su defensa y utilizar sus armas contra ellos. En cuanto nos "
"descubran, todo el pueblo nos atacará."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/intro_08"
msgid "Secondly, we have to free our men. We can't let them die here."
msgstr ""
"En segundo lugar, tenemos que liberar a nuestros hombres. No podemos dejar "
"que mueran aquí."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/intro_09"
msgid ""
"And another thing: I saw a Soviet officer with a briefcase in this village. "
"I wouldn't mind taking a look at the papers inside. They could explain why "
"Russians control this village. I need to be the one to read those documents, "
"since I am the only one in the squad who understands Russian."
msgstr ""
"Y otra cosa: vi a un oficial soviético con un maletín en este pueblo. No me "
"importaría echar un vistazo a los papeles que hay dentro. Podrían explicar "
"por qué los rusos controlan esta aldea. Tengo que ser yo quien lea esos "
"documentos, ya que soy el único de la brigada que entiende ruso."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/jagdpanther_repaired"
msgid ""
"Outstanding work, soldiers. Armor like that will take us all the way to "
"Moscow. But be careful with it, this beast is the only one we've got."
msgstr ""
"Excelente trabajo, soldados. Un blindaje así nos llevará hasta Moscú. Pero "
"hay que cuidarlo, esta bestia es la única que tenemos."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/pow_free"
msgid ""
"Good day, men. We thought you could use some help. You are now temporarily "
"under my command."
msgstr ""
"Buenos días. Hemos pensado que os vendría bien algo de ayuda. Ahora estáis "
"temporalmente bajo mi mando."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/secret"
msgid ""
"What did I tell you guys? This dinner was indeed worth the hunt! Just like "
"the good old days!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué os había dicho? ¡Esta cena sí que mereció la pena! ¡Como en los viejos "
"tiempos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/officer/see_jagdpanther"
msgid ""
"What a surprise. I didn't expect to see them so soon on the Ostfront. If we "
"capture and repair this vehicle, it will give us a huge advantage."
msgstr ""
"Menuda sorpresa. No esperaba verlos tan pronto en el Ostfront. Si capturamos "
"y reparamos este vehículo, nos dará una gran ventaja."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/rus/intro_01"
msgid "Hey you, leave your cars and come over here with your hands up!"
msgstr "¡Eh, vosotros, dejad los coches y venid aquí con las manos en alto!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/soldier/docs_found"
msgid "Look! There are some papers here..."
msgstr "¡Mira! Aquí hay unos papeles..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/soldier/enemy_reinf_north"
msgid "Watch out, they have reinforcements coming from the north!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado, vienen refuerzos del norte!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/soldier/enemy_reinf_west"
msgid "Watch out, they have reinforcements approaching from the west!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado, se acercan refuerzos desde el oeste!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/soldier/intro_01"
msgid "I can't argue with that... It reminds me of my village."
msgstr "No puedo discutirlo... Me recuerda a mi pueblo."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/soldier/intro_02"
msgid "What is this?"
msgstr "¿Que es esto?"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/soldier/intro_03"
msgid "What the hell is going on there?"
msgstr "¿Qué demonios está pasando ahí?"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/soldier/intro_04"
msgid ""
"Damn them! And I thought that the front line was twenty kilometers from here!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos sean! ¡Y yo que pensaba que el frente estaba a veinte kilómetros "
"de aquí!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/soldier/jagdpanther"
msgid ""
"Hauptmann Hellmann, look! The Russians have something that is rightfully "
"ours."
msgstr "Hauptmann Hellmann, ¡mira! Los rusos tienen algo que nos pertenece."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/narrator/soldier/officer_dead"
msgid "Hauptmann Hellmann was killed! We need to get out of here now!"
msgstr "¡Han matado al Hauptmann Hellmann! ¡Tenemos que salir de aquí ya!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Congratulations, you did it! You showed great improvisation skills here. "
"Your actions today will surely get you promoted. Well done!"
msgstr ""
"¡Enhorabuena, lo has conseguido! Has demostrado una gran capacidad de "
"improvisación. Tus acciones de hoy seguramente te harán ascender. "
"¡Enhorabuena!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"That was not what we planned for. You’ll have to regroup, go in again, and "
"try different tactics; giving up is not an option for our captured friends."
msgstr ""
"Eso no era lo que habíamos planeado. Tendrás que reagruparte, entrar de "
"nuevo e intentar tácticas diferentes; rendirse no es una opción para "
"nuestros amigos capturados."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/place"
msgid "Elements of the 4th Panzer Army"
msgstr "Elementos del 4º Ejército Panzer"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/01_pow"
msgid "Free the German POWs"
msgstr "Liberar a los prisioneros de guerra alemanes"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/02_docs"
msgid "Recover and analyze the Soviet HQ documents"
msgstr "Recuperar y analizar los documentos del Cuartel General soviético"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/03_officer"
msgid ""
"Dietrich Hellmann must survive. He's the only one who can read the Soviet "
"documents."
msgstr ""
"Dietrich Hellmann debe sobrevivir. Es el único que puede leer los documentos "
"soviéticos."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/04_ambush"
msgid "Prepare an ambush"
msgstr "Prepara una emboscada"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/05_evac"
msgid "Reach the evacuation point"
msgstr "Llega al punto de evacuación"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/opt01_repair"
msgid "Recapture the Jagdpanther and repair it"
msgstr "Recupera el Jagdpanther y repáralo"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/opt02_allround"
msgid "<c(B29557)>All-Round doctrine:</c> Eliminate the enemy sniper"
msgstr "<c(B29557)>Doctrina integral:</c> Eliminar al francotirador enemigo"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/opt02_defensive"
msgid ""
"<c(B29557)>Defensive doctrine:</c> Eliminate the Soviet light armor unit in "
"the village"
msgstr ""
"<c(B29557)>Doctrina defensiva:</c> Eliminar la unidad de blindados ligeros "
"soviéticos en la aldea"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/opt02_irregular"
msgid "<c(B29557)>Irregular doctrine:</c> Eliminate 2 enemy units with a knife"
msgstr ""
"<c(B29557)>Doctrina irregular:</c> Elimina 2 unidades enemigas con un "
"cuchillo"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/opt02_offensive"
msgid ""
"<c(B29557)>Offensive doctrine:</c> Eliminate 5 enemy units with a "
"flamethrower"
msgstr ""
"<c(B29557)>Doctrina ofensiva:</c> Elimina 5 unidades enemigas con un "
"lanzallamas"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/secret01_lunch"
msgid "Secret objective #1"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/tasks/secret01_lunch_completed"
msgid "Secret objective #1: Bring a piece of chicken to the field kitchen"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1: Llevar un trozo de pollo a la cocina del campo"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/ui/doctrine_unit_allround"
msgid "<c(B29557)>All-Round:</c> Sniper"
msgstr "<c(B29557)>Todoterreno:</c> Francotirador"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/ui/doctrine_unit_defensive"
msgid "<c(B29557)>Defensive:</c> AT Rifleman"
msgstr "<c(B29557)>Defensiva:</c> Fusilero AT"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/ui/doctrine_unit_irregular"
msgid "<c(B29557)>Irregular:</c> Scouts"
msgstr "<c(B29557)>Irregular:</c> Exploradores"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1944_03_trap/ui/doctrine_unit_offensive"
msgid "<c(B29557)>Offensive:</c> Flamethrower"
msgstr "<c(B29557)>Ofensiva:</c> Lanzallamas"

